---
// src/pages/bet.astro
// Quest Labs · /bet · Bet on Our Becoming
---

<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Bet on Our Becoming · Quest Labs</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Wish you could do something to materially shift the trajectory of a wayward world? Bet on our becoming. Fund the futures work that matters." />
  <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/global.css" />
</head>
<body>

  <!-- Nav (mirrors site structure) -->
  <header>
    <nav>
      <a href="/" class="logo-link">
        <img src="/quest-labs-logo.png" alt="Quest Labs" class="logo" />
      </a>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="/program">FLIP</a></li>
        <li><a href="/educators">Educators</a></li>
        <li><a href="/foundations">Foundations</a></li>
        <li><a href="/black-menagerie">Black Menagerie</a></li>
        <li><a href="/about">About</a></li>
        <li><a href="/contact">Contact</a></li>
        <li><a href="/bet" class="nav-active">Bet</a></li>
      </ul>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <main class="bet-page">

    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="bet-hero">
      <p class="eyebrow">Quest Labs · Bet on Our Becoming</p>
      <h1>Bet on our becoming.</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        Wish you could do something to materially shift the trajectory of a wayward world driven by nefarious nonsense? You can. This is how.
      </p>
      <p class="hero-body">
        Quest Labs is fueled by <strong>FAITH</strong> — and by people who believe that real change starts in the body, the community, and the classroom long before it shows up in the news.
      </p>
      <div class="faith-reveal" aria-label="FAITH: Finding Alternative Innovative Transformative Heartspaces">
        <div class="faith-item" tabindex="0">
          <span class="faith-item-letter" aria-hidden="true">F</span>
          <div class="faith-item-text">
            <span class="faith-item-word">Finding</span>
            <span class="faith-item-gloss">the quest is active — we are always seeking</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faith-item" tabindex="0">
          <span class="faith-item-letter" aria-hidden="true">A</span>
          <div class="faith-item-text">
            <span class="faith-item-word">Alternative</span>
            <span class="faith-item-gloss">futures that haven't been imagined yet</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faith-item" tabindex="0">
          <span class="faith-item-letter" aria-hidden="true">I</span>
          <div class="faith-item-text">
            <span class="faith-item-word">Innovative</span>
            <span class="faith-item-gloss">open innovation, co-created with community</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faith-item" tabindex="0">
          <span class="faith-item-letter" aria-hidden="true">T</span>
          <div class="faith-item-text">
            <span class="faith-item-word">Transformative</span>
            <span class="faith-item-gloss">personal and social transformation, both at once</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faith-item" tabindex="0">
          <span class="faith-item-letter" aria-hidden="true">H</span>
          <div class="faith-item-text">
            <span class="faith-item-word">Heartspaces</span>
            <span class="faith-item-gloss">lead with the heart — head follows</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="faith-hint">hover each letter · tap on mobile</p>
      </div>
      <p class="hero-body">
        You're not buying a product. You're betting on a future we haven't fully seen yet — but one we feel, and one our future ancestors are going to want to have been part of.
      </p>
    </section>

    <hr class="section-rule" />

    <!-- Tiers -->
    <section class="tiers-section">
      <p class="section-label">Choose your bet</p>

      <!-- Tier 1: The Spark -->
      <div class="tier-card">
        <div class="tier-header">
          <div class="tier-symbol">◯</div>
          <div class="tier-title-block">
            <h2 class="tier-name">The Spark</h2>
            <p class="tier-tagline">One light. One life. One ripple.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="tier-price">$500</div>
        </div>
        <p class="tier-desc">
          Fund one participant's place in a 12-week Quest Labs cohort. Name someone specific, or leave the seat open for whoever needs it most. A single spark is how every fire starts.
        </p>
        <div class="tier-actions">
          <a href="https://www.paypal.com/ncp/payment/6DCPDYTQT536A" class="pay-btn" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            Bet $500 via PayPal →
          </a>
          <div class="qr-wrap">
            <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="QR code for Sponsor a seat — Quest Labs" class="qr-code" />
            <p class="qr-label">or scan to pay</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Tier 2: The Pair -->
      <div class="tier-card tier-featured">
        <div class="tier-header">
          <div class="tier-symbol">◆</div>
          <div class="tier-title-block">
            <h2 class="tier-name">The Pair</h2>
            <p class="tier-tagline">Two lights travel further.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="tier-price">$1,000</div>
        </div>
        <p class="tier-desc">
          Because transformation runs deeper in pairs. Two seats, fully flexible — same cohort or different, your call or theirs. Send them to anyone, anytime. No strings.
        </p>
        <div class="tier-actions">
          <a href="https://www.paypal.com/ncp/payment/ZLWJJH3EVH4MJ" class="pay-btn" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            Bet $1,000 via PayPal →
          </a>
          <div class="qr-wrap">
            <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="QR code for Sponsor a dyad — Quest Labs" class="qr-code" />
            <p class="qr-label">or scan to pay</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Tier 3: The Constellation -->
      <div class="tier-card">
        <div class="tier-header">
          <div class="tier-symbol">◈</div>
          <div class="tier-title-block">
            <h2 class="tier-name">The Constellation</h2>
            <p class="tier-tagline">A pattern emerges.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="tier-price">$5,000</div>
        </div>
        <p class="tier-desc">
          Ten seats for a school, a team, a community you believe in. Enough to shift a staff room, a department, a cohort of educators. This is where institutional change starts — not in policy, but in people.
        </p>
        <div class="tier-actions">
          <a href="https://www.paypal.com/ncp/payment/GR3WJPK28RWZ4" class="pay-btn" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            Bet $5,000 via PayPal →
          </a>
          <div class="qr-wrap">
            <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="QR code for Bring a team — Quest Labs" class="qr-code" />
            <p class="qr-label">or scan to pay</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Tier 4: The Universe -->
      <div class="tier-card">
        <div class="tier-header">
          <div class="tier-symbol">◎</div>
          <div class="tier-title-block">
            <h2 class="tier-name">The Universe</h2>
            <p class="tier-tagline">You seed the whole thing.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="tier-price">$10,000</div>
        </div>
        <p class="tier-desc">
          Foundation-level partnership. You fund an entire cohort from the ground up — and you don't disappear when the check clears. This tier comes with real-time, collaborative documentation of the work as it unfolds: participant-voiced, Quest Labs-curated, the good-news feed we all desperately need.
        </p>
        <ul class="tier-perks">
          <li>Named cohort sponsorship</li>
          <li>Collaborative real-time updates from participants + Quest Labs team</li>
          <li>Positive social documentation — living proof something extraordinary is happening</li>
          <li>Direct line to the Quest Labs founders throughout the cohort</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="tier-actions">
          <a href="https://www.paypal.com/ncp/payment/RAHEVMFETBX4U" class="pay-btn" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            Bet $10,000 via PayPal →
          </a>
          <div class="qr-wrap">
            <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="QR code for Fund a cohort — Quest Labs" class="qr-code" />
            <p class="qr-label">or scan to pay</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Tier 5: The Wish -->
      <div class="tier-card">
        <div class="tier-header">
          <div class="tier-symbol">✦</div>
          <div class="tier-title-block">
            <h2 class="tier-name">The Wish</h2>
            <p class="tier-tagline">As you wish.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="tier-price">Any amount</div>
        </div>
        <p class="tier-desc">
          You know what feels right. Every contribution goes directly into keeping this work alive, accessible, and audacious. No amount is too small to matter.
        </p>
        <div class="tier-actions">
          <a href="https://www.paypal.com/ncp/payment/XKNZVQHFY7QYJ" class="pay-btn" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            Make a wish via PayPal →
          </a>
          <div class="qr-wrap">
            <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="QR code for As you wish — Quest Labs" class="qr-code" />
            <p class="qr-label">or scan to pay</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </section>

    <hr class="section-rule" />

    <!-- Closing -->
    <section class="bet-closing">
      <p>
        For larger partnerships, institutional funding, or conversations about embedding Quest Labs in your world —
        <a href="/contact">let's talk</a>.
      </p>
      <p class="closing-sub">Word for 2026: <em>audacious.</em> Welcome to it.</p>
    </section>

  </main>

  <!-- Footer (mirrors site structure) -->
  <footer>
    <div class="footer-inner">
      <p class="footer-brand">Quest Labs</p>
      <p class="footer-sub">Healing-Centered Futures</p>
      <nav class="footer-nav">
        <a href="/program">FLIP</a>
        <a href="/educators">Educators</a>
        <a href="/foundations">Foundations</a>
        <a href="/black-menagerie">Black Menagerie</a>
        <a href="/about">About</a>
        <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
      </nav>
      <p class="footer-copy">2026 Quest Labs · Makeda · All futures reserved · Berlin &amp; Beyond</p>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <script>
    document.querySelectorAll('.faith-item').forEach(item => {
      item.addEventListener('click', () => {
        item.classList.toggle('active');
      });
    });
  </script>

</body>
</html>

<style>
  /* ── Bet page styles ── */
  /* These extend your global.css — adjust tokens to match your site vars */

  .bet-page {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 4rem 1.5rem 5rem;
  }

  /* Hero */
  .bet-hero {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    opacity: 0.5;
    margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
  }

  .bet-hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
  }

  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
    max-width: 58ch;
  }

  .hero-body {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
    max-width: 58ch;
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  /* FAITH block — Treatment C: hover to reveal */
  .faith-reveal {
    margin: 2rem 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2px;
  }

  .faith-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0;
    cursor: default;
    outline: none;
  }

  .faith-item-letter {
    font-size: 3.75rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1;
    width: 4rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    opacity: 0.12;
    transition: opacity 0.25s ease;
  }

  .faith-item-text {
    overflow: hidden;
    max-height: 0;
    opacity: 0;
    padding-left: 0.5rem;
    transition: max-height 0.3s ease, opacity 0.25s ease;
  }

  .faith-item:hover .faith-item-letter,
  .faith-item:focus .faith-item-letter {
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .faith-item:hover .faith-item-text,
  .faith-item:focus .faith-item-text {
    max-height: 80px;
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .faith-item-word {
    display: block;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .faith-item-gloss {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    opacity: 0.5;
    margin-top: 2px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .faith-hint {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    opacity: 0.3;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin: 0.25rem 0 0 0.25rem;
  }

  /* Mobile: tap to toggle */
  @media (hover: none) {
    .faith-item.active .faith-item-letter { opacity: 1; }
    .faith-item.active .faith-item-text { max-height: 80px; opacity: 1; }
  }

  /* Rules */
  .section-rule {
    border: none;
    border-top: 1px solid currentColor;
    opacity: 0.12;
    margin: 3rem 0;
  }

  /* Tiers */
  .section-label {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    opacity: 0.5;
    margin: 0 0 2rem;
  }

  .tier-card {
    border: 1px solid currentColor;
    border-opacity: 0.15;
    border-radius: 2px;
    padding: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    position: relative;
    opacity: 1;
  }

  /* Use outline style matching site's card aesthetic */
  .tier-card {
    outline: 1px solid rgba(128,128,128,0.2);
    border: none;
  }

  .tier-featured {
    outline: 2px solid currentColor;
    outline-opacity: 0.6;
  }

  .tier-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .tier-symbol {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    opacity: 0.4;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    padding-top: 2px;
  }

  .tier-title-block {
    flex: 1;
  }

  .tier-name {
    font-size: 1.35rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin: 0 0 2px;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .tier-tagline {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    opacity: 0.5;
    margin: 0;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .tier-price {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    white-space: nowrap;
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  .tier-desc {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    opacity: 0.75;
    margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
    max-width: 56ch;
  }

  .tier-perks {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
  }

  .tier-perks li {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    opacity: 0.65;
    padding: 0.2rem 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .tier-perks li::before {
    content: "· ";
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  /* Actions row */
  .tier-actions {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .pay-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.65rem 1.35rem;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    text-decoration: none;
    border: 1px solid currentColor;
    border-radius: 2px;
    transition: opacity 0.15s ease;
  }

  .pay-btn:hover {
    opacity: 0.65;
  }

  /* QR code */
  .qr-wrap {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 4px;
  }

  .qr-code {
    width: 72px;
    height: 72px;
    display: block;
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  .qr-label {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    opacity: 0.4;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* Closing */
  .bet-closing {
    max-width: 52ch;
  }

  .bet-closing p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    opacity: 0.75;
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
  }

  .bet-closing a {
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
  }

  .closing-sub {
    font-size: 0.8rem !important;
    opacity: 0.4 !important;
    margin-top: 1.5rem !important;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  /* Nav active state */
  .nav-active {
    opacity: 1 !important;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 540px) {
    .bet-page {
      padding: 2.5rem 1.25rem 4rem;
    }

    .tier-card {
      padding: 1.5rem 1.25rem;
    }

    .tier-header {
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .tier-price {
      width: 100%;
      margin-left: 2.5rem;
      margin-top: -0.5rem;
    }

    .tier-actions {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }
  }
</style>
